{
  "stem": "9538.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they passed a law, all those who were-- going at the time, I was told, passed a law that those who were soldiers in the first World War should be released immediately.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father came home after a few weeks from Buchenwald, and so did a few others who were also soldiers in the first World War.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the others had to stay for much longer in Buchenwald under terrible conditions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were not allowed to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were pressed to emigrate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Germans didn't want to keep the Jews in Germany anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whoever had a chance to emigrate emigrated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My poor father went to Hamburg-- that's one of the Hansa towns-- to get an affidavit for Siam.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When I hear 'The King and I,' I think often, pull the affidavit my poor father got for the family to go to Siam.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the only one where the Jews could still go more or less immediately.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise you would have to have visas and there was-- to America, you had to-- there was a-- was a waiting list.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you had to wait your quota and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Siam would accept you more or less immediately.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Siam we were supposed to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But now to go to Siam, you have to sell your stuff.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to prepare.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by-- by the time we were ready to go to Siam, the war had broken out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've got the pictures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's the only picture of him was he was shaven, and-- his head was shaven, and he was tortured.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because he stood up, he said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the wardens were Germans and Poles, which we later encountered in the-- encountered in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
